meaning.en: Of or expressed in a symbol or symbols.
meaning.vi: Hỗ trợ hoặc hỗ trợ trang bị nội thất.

sentences.en: There are several symbolic acts descriptive of the siege.

sentences.en: It will be shown later that all invariants, single or simultaneous, are expressible in terms of symbolic products.
